{"title":"制鞋工人颂革新","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"制鞋工人颂革新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自古做鞋手工操，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锥子鎯头和大刀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工具笨重产量少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上鞋工人累弯腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今使用土机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干起活来轻又巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布鞋增产好几倍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢党的好领导。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}